BT /F2 16 Tf 1 0 0 1 54 750 Tm (1. Executive Summary) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 1 0 0 1 54 728 Tm (DiabetesInsight is a machine learning based Streamlit application that estimates) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 1 0 0 1 54 712 Tm (diabetes risk from user-provided health indicators. The project combines a clean) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 1 0 0 1 54 696 Tm (browser interface, a trained scikit-learn pipeline, and CSV-backed persistence to) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 1 0 0 1 54 680 Tm (create a compact academic demonstration of predictive analytics in healthcare.) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 1 0 0 1 54 654 Tm (The system is designed for project evaluation, local demonstration, and basic) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 1 0 0 1 54 638 Tm (cloud deployment. It guides a user from login to prediction, shows a) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 1 0 0 1 54 622 Tm (probability-based result, and stores the latest prediction details in a simple) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 1 0 0 1 54 606 Tm (tabular file.) Tj ET
BT /F2 16 Tf 1 0 0 1 54 580 Tm (2. Project Objectives) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 1 0 0 1 54 558 Tm (- Predict diabetes risk from commonly used medical and demographic features.) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 1 0 0 1 54 542 Tm (- Provide a simple and attractive interface that can be used by non-technical) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 1 0 0 1 54 526 Tm (evaluators.) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 1 0 0 1 54 510 Tm (- Compare multiple machine learning models and keep the best one.) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 1 0 0 1 54 494 Tm (- Store user details and the latest prediction in a lightweight CSV file.) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 1 0 0 1 54 478 Tm (- Keep the project easy to deploy on platforms such as Streamlit Cloud or) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 1 0 0 1 54 462 Tm (Render.) Tj ET
BT /F2 16 Tf 1 0 0 1 54 436 Tm (3. Problem Statement) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 1 0 0 1 54 414 Tm (Early diabetes screening is important because many patients do not recognize) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 1 0 0 1 54 398 Tm (warning signs until the disease has already progressed. A lightweight prediction) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 1 0 0 1 54 382 Tm (system can help demonstrate how machine learning can support screening by) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 1 0 0 1 54 366 Tm (identifying risk patterns from historical health data.) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 1 0 0 1 54 340 Tm (This project does not replace clinical diagnosis. It is an academic) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 1 0 0 1 54 324 Tm (decision-support prototype that shows how data preprocessing, model training,) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 1 0 0 1 54 308 Tm (inference, and user-facing presentation can be combined into one application.) Tj ET
BT /F2 16 Tf 1 0 0 1 54 282 Tm (4. Technology Stack) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 1 0 0 1 54 260 Tm (- Frontend and UI: Streamlit) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 1 0 0 1 54 244 Tm (- Programming Language: Python) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 1 0 0 1 54 228 Tm (- Data Handling: pandas) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 1 0 0 1 54 212 Tm (- Machine Learning: scikit-learn) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 1 0 0 1 54 196 Tm (- Model Serialization: joblib) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 1 0 0 1 54 180 Tm (- Environment Configuration: python-dotenv) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 1 0 0 1 54 164 Tm (- Optional API Layer: FastAPI and Uvicorn) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 1 0 0 1 54 148 Tm (- Deployment Support: Streamlit Cloud and Render) Tj ET
BT /F2 16 Tf 1 0 0 1 54 122 Tm (5. Project Structure) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 1 0 0 1 54 100 Tm (----------------------------------------) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 1 0 0 1 54 86 Tm (diabetes-ai/) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 1 0 0 1 54 70 Tm (|-- app.py) Tj ET
endstream
endobj
